/>\n<br />\n荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅燈區點玩，有無吸大麻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲女著住底衫褲企係間鋪入面 玻璃隔住 應該就咁行入去就可以幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c15e4ce20ea93eb7fb9f4d8657758fdf2a0a9a","tid":8371,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>total 洗費幾多？預算幾多？over咗幾多？有冇係果邊做嘢？本地邊間U？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9萬鬆啲 除左學費包晒住宿機票生活費旅行<br />\n同budget差唔多 冇做野 CU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed070d142f24d7cbd69f9fee060b6de7f5c79143","tid":8371,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識既多數係local 定exchange students?<br />\n自己去定有同學一齊?<br />\n住dorm 定租屋? 住dorm 既話個到啲氣氛點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住dorm 我果棟係for exchange students<br />\n所以識exchange students仲多 <br />\n氣氛幾好 同層果啲通常都會識晒 夜晚有時會一齊吹下水玩啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5455c21d1d5d826728db279ba7744034ec1bd39a","tid":8371,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前去英國exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣天氣凍就諗番嗰度啲日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲好記得冬天四點黑晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果種無憂無慮淨係諗去邊度玩既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7037588b4d8fa7a0a222fd13a92b9294d8a3c7e8","tid":8371,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年前去英國exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣天氣凍就諗番嗰度啲日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲好記得冬天四點黑晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果種無憂無慮淨係諗去邊度玩既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時想就坐車去下海邊食下蠔<br />\n得閒就買枝酒返屋企飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4423e74416a8bf854a135da3ed36148bd99b59","tid":8371,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荷蘭治安點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 物價貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n治安幾好 除左有啲人會偷單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少少貴 出街食可能50-60蚊起至百幾蚊不等 但香港人應該afford到 同埋自己煮可以30蚊內一餐<br />\n不過搭車就好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歐洲普遍都係咁"},{"pid":"58fa6c8b3f0e6a75dedcb613ccaf1bf450f7110d","tid":8371,"uid":26045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"去邊間？"},{"pid":"3dc6eb66abc79f47ada836efb0635995d16f5f5c","tid":8371,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識既多數係local 定exchange students?<br />\n自己去定有同學一齊?<br />\n住dorm 定租屋? 住dorm 既話個到啲氣氛點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住dorm 我果棟係for exchange students<br />\n所以識exchange students仲多 <br />\n氣氛幾好 同層果啲通常都會識晒 夜晚有時會一齊吹下水玩啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就黎去瑞典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我個到既dorm 無分exchange/local 不過我諗都係識返exchange 多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64609cd7aed9d89ee44bc1f5e2487